Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The manager has lost his golden watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That man you brought is the real thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ian! The thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't tell to the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However I will inevitably catch him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,DETECTING THE INNOCENCE OF IAN!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To the degree the birds come\Nand they are reassuring to Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On his shoulders and on his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh...?!\N- Eh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How many birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How many birds...?\NIn any case it were many!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we ask about the number of birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe six... maybe not, five!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This number is not great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean the birds are flying around\NIan and it is reassuring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! The trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time Ian seemed as big as trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But is not that man a thief?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from my father that\Nhe had stolen from the bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This time he stole a golden watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My father and mother told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...he's very dangerous and\NI shouldn't approach him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Scotland Yard came here too to catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I met Ian, I felt that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that person was terrifying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's painful to misunderstand him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think Ian is a bad person!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I also don't think he is a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As John said,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,birds and animals can tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It knows who is a good person,\Nand who is a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't be fooled by only the forms of people!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Animals can't be fooled at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh...?\N- Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Every serious thing is always true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Birds don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem that Ian is a bad man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,People can't be judged by their appearances!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian, you're not a bank robber, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remain silent, Ian,\Nthe others won't understand you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were wrong, you said to them,\N"You are wrong"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you explained them directly, Ian,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone will understand that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm working now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you explain it to others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Has a big problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakfast will be ready soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry but... Can you deliver lunch to your\Nfather in the mine on your way to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, but why two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One for your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other for Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But why Ian doesn't explain it to others?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,John.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,John, do you think Ian will relax\Nwhen he tells to the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that he doesn't speak\Nmuch with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he doesn't speak,\Nhe won't be believed by the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, John...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian continued to work hard and didn't left,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in spite of the rumors spread about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's not worried about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, this is what you\Nthink isn't your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I rely on you, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, good morning, John! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other... is it for Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother made it for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Make everyone understand Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Dad! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to the forest again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The knife is for making these!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Ian...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that person a little while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A button...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, put it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...to leave you in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We can process the things you want slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These must be designed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian Cooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,28 years old, from Yorkshire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we'll search your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The gold watch of the manager\NDuhan of Wellington Mine was stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose is this clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You found it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In this man's room...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the clock is stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is Ian...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Walter... continue from manager Duhan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We will investigate this guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next king was James I.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}James was the father of Mary Stuart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Queen Elizabeth died,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was no successor then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to the descendants of the\NKing of England, the King of Stewart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is! This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has my initials here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a souvenir from my grandfather, who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very precious to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday evening you got\Nsome very aggressive advice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,from Mr. Carraclough, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have found the directory instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We will take the rest of the\Npurposes here to investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We may find another evidence against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, he participated\Nin the bank robbery!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Walter, take it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey stop it! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dangerous dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wise to let such a dog free?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?\NIt wasn't like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One of you... one of you bring a strand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Lassie's not here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't Lassie come yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not its habit not to come with John.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He always asked me in my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, the latest thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The police arrested Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not clear? You are detained!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get to the main office\Nyou can recognize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just the watch, but your other actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was the watch inside my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to know the truth, Mr. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ian!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't approach this dangerous man, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you do something bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have become close\Nto a great liar, Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And now go in! Go in immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the clock in Ian's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered, when Ian was outside his room...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this button in his room\Nwhen someone entered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him in quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,John, have you entered his room\Nwithout his permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's wrong but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the most important thing\Nis what happened next!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Do it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,John, you mean that this button belongs\Nto the person who entered the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Probably!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,John, give me the button\Nto let Lassie to smell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you moved yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, look now for the button holder!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait until we check more Ian's arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- The arrest for the golden watch!\N- Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The police of England will close\Nthe search file for the offender
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because the real criminal is in our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We did something great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's the same button!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with my luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you did something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:16:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to harass me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use force, you will be transferred\Nto the public administration
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to receive your punishment, Mr. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you don't want to wear\Nthe aggressor's clothes in front of your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time... The person who entered\NIan's room is you, you hysterical, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Dohan's golden watch has been\Nplaced by you in Ian's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was under the bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see you, though...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you teach your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does accuse others\Nof criminality without evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is you, Mr. Carraclough! Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I mean, this issue is different?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There is even an evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same button that was in Ian's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have fallen from me\Nwhen I investigated him earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that you have no evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian is the golden clock thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Detective!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I also thought it wasn't right\Nthat we should seize him like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Walter, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian is doomed to steal the bank originally!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it is a criminal case,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian hasn't committed any crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is this the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I also thought he was the real thief!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also that bank robbery
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is suspected of being done by a gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Silent, Walter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian didn't steal the golden watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh...?\N- Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the clock in the office drawer\Nof manager Duhan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You infiltrated into Ian's room\Nand putting it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood, if that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Walter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to the head office!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian Cooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I still think you were at the bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the cuffs off of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Walter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me lose my temper\Nmore, you villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The band of the bank robbers was caught!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This story explains!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the story of Ian's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of me, Ian was\Naccused without being guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not it better to keep him doing his work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have told you from the start\Nthat Ian can't be the bank robber!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I trusted him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a good man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I want to see him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Dr. Hooper went to catch\Nfish, he was seriously injured!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried to save him, but I couldn't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie, you are the only one\Nwho can tell to the villagers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\NHURRY! SAVE DR. HOOPER{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
